ts/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n十足十支那啲網絡小說"},{"pid":"4778df779a76a680c44dd19edd79abdd9d36a5ac","tid":330082,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"古天樂普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得睇黑社會，條撚樣講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09201c58e64f3ea3e5978eb87fa436d33da9168","tid":330082,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盛唐三部曲咁都完唔到尾, 黃易RIP, 我諗遲D會搵人代筆收尾, 雖然呢套野去到第二, 三部已經唔好睇了</blockquote><br />\n反而覺得第一部唔好睇，道心種魔練到一半已經屈晒機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到第三部符太做太醫寫醫錄先覺得好睇<br />\n出版社好似講左話出晒存稿就算，唔會搵人代寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bdf4c32a97c2936a06f8c119231cf6bbca0b70","tid":330082,"uid":22390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"你去一個國家岀席活動 要求人地用你自己既語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你去日本會唔會叫佢講普通話？<br />\n<br />\n古仔表演得又幾好 完美撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f5ea87f21af4e1a3893c695af75021e9d39138","tid":330082,"uid":2203,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"你真的還站起來"},{"pid":"feb6d0f47478c03e2d8dcdb52a7c1351b922d898","tid":330082,"uid":97626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"龍鷹係咁屈就唔洗死第二次啦 <br />\n<br />\n有幾個好打過佢"}]}